query:
INSERT INTO ven (
                id,
                created_date_time,
                modification_date_time,
                ven_name,
                attributes,
                targets
            )
            VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), now(), now(), $1, $2, $3)
            RETURNING
                id,
                created_date_time,
                modification_date_time,
                ven_name,
                attributes,
                targets
